snippet.title: Vampire Rancher Gameplay Trailer
snippet.description:
The first gameplay trailer for Vampire Rancher.

Rancher by day, Vampire by night. Manage your time and resources to restore your sleepy little town to its former glory, all while satisfying your vampire needs for blood. Oversee shops and saloons, farm crops and humans, and explore ancient vampiric ruins in the Weird Wild West!

Wishlist on Steam: https://bit.ly/VampireRancherSteam
